Package: newEuropeReviewR
Title: The New Europe Review data archive (1916-1920)
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Stanislav",
    family = "Pejša",
    email = "stanislavpejsa@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5057-262X"))
Description: This R data package contains a text corpus of articles from 
    the complete run of the foreign policy weekly _The New Europe_, 
    published between 1916 and 1920, together with bibliographic metadata 
    and country frequency counts derived from the corpus.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
